^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, that hand can be made, but let me discuss the bidding first. First, why Patti has a splinter. Once Dee shows hearts Patti has 19 Dummy Points. 14 HCP, 2 points for two quality suits, and three for a singleton with 4 trumps. If Dee has 14 in support of hearts. It is just enough for slam.|
