NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Additionally, if Dee has no wasted values in diamonds, that makes slam a reasonable proposition. The only fly in the ointment that I mentioned, is the of double of 2C which  makes the Queen of clubs rather suspect. So, I might just bid 4H, but 4D certainly had merit.|
